                <p class="as_font14 as_padderTop20 as_padderBottom_a20 revealy" style="text-align: justify;text-justify: inter-word;"><b>Scorpio (October 23 - November 21):</b> As fall deepens, Scorpio emerges as the intense water sign symbolized by the Scorpion. Scorpio individuals are passionate, mysterious, and fiercely loyal, with a depth of emotion that few can match. Ruled by Pluto, the planet of transformation, Scorpio is drawn to the darker aspects of life and is not afraid to delve into the depths of the psyche. They are perceptive, intuitive individuals who value authenticity and depth in all relationships.</p>
